  "description": "<p> 安装了Windows 8.1预览版的用户或许会发现，当他们试图通过将一个Modern/Metro拖拽到屏幕底部来关闭的时候，该应用或许仍留存于任务管理器里面。<strong>在Windows 8.1预览版中，如果想要彻底关闭一个应用，需要在将应用拖拽到屏幕底部后(这点与Windows 8一样)，继续\"Hold住\"，直到应用的瓷贴变回了LOGO。</strong>Win8上的老方法或许会不太好用。<br /> </p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e034b61/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242983.htm&amp;t=%E5%BD%BB%E5%BA%95%E5%85%B3%E9%97%ADWindows+8.1%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242983.htm&amp;t=%E5%BD%BB%E5%BA%95%E5%85%B3%E9%97%ADWindows+8.1%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242983.htm&amp;t=%E5%BD%BB%E5%BA%95%E5%85%B3%E9%97%ADWindows+8.1%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242983.htm&amp;t=%E5%BD%BB%E5%BA%95%E5%85%B3%E9%97%ADWindows+8.1%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242983.htm&amp